{
  "texts": [
    "Academic abstracts.",
    "Academic abstract (AA) is a condensed version of an entire article.",
    "It is usually a brief, natural, complete text and a meaningful way to promote academic viewpoints.",
    "Due to the interdisciplinary differences in the convention and style of abstract writing (Li, 2020), we collected academic abstracts exclusively within translation studies.",
    "The reason for choosing this discipline is that the translators of the abstracts, also as the researchers of translation studies, could consciously manipulate the translation process."
  ]
}